{"tid":249444,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"前十字韌帶斷裂(ACL injury) 手術一問","createTime":"2017-05-19T10:00:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-18T12:24:50.000Z","uid":32528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c76b409a988e991be41fccc8b7a06017dfbfaf79","tid":249444,"uid":32528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T10:00:05.000Z","msg":"想問多d前十字韌帶手術既野<br />\n風險 復康 之後運動能力等等<br />\n<br />\n平時打波多 早前醫生話前十字完全斷裂(compete rupture)  google左仲係好擔心 有無人可以分享下"},{"pid":"e5cd051c5fcd5d4432ffc172be4a198489ca6e17","tid":249444,"uid":29229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T10:05:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問多d前十字韌帶手術既野<br />\n風險 復康 之後運動能力等等<br />\n<br />\n平時打波多 早前醫生話前十字完全斷裂(compete rupture)  google左仲係好擔心 有無人可以分享下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果你係complete rupture <br />\n咁基本上想做番運動就一定要做手術架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n風險都係全身麻醉會有既風險 同埋有機會影響到隻腳某啲神經線既感知能力<br />\n<br />\n不過你放心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 絕大部份做完手術既都可以去番未受傷前既水平 大概半年 <br />\n睇你做物理治療既進度 勤唔勤力"},{"pid":"b654b7d93e2883e73604c44214c23f578f1949bc","tid":249444,"uid":32528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T10:06:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想問多d前十字韌帶手術既野<br />\n風險 復康 之後運動能力等等<br />\n<br />\n平時打波多 早前醫生話前十字完全斷裂(compete rupture)  google左仲係好擔心 有無人可以分享下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果你係complete rupture <br />\n咁基本上想做番運動就一定要做手術架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n風險都係全身麻醉會有既風險 同埋有機會影響到隻腳某啲神經線既感知能力<br />\n<br />\n不過你放心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 絕大部份做完手術既都可以去番未受傷前既水平 大概半年 <br />\n睇你做物理治療既進度 勤唔勤力</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n即係大部分風險係麻醉既風險?<br />\n影響神經果part可唔可以講多d thanks thanks"},{"pid":"4789b4ae930498c51a09ee5a586f778bfb0a3010","tid":249444,"uid":69159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T10:19:17.000Z","msg":"裂左之後，你要預左唔可以超越以前既狀態，因為會再裂開<br />\n但慢慢一步一步黎 可以回復而家既水平<br />\n無咩風險 可能係做完手術後唔慣之類 <br />\n一兩個月順利行到 半年內做得返運動<br />\n不過我就大約一年先完全正常(強烈都唔會痛)"},{"pid":"645ba7190534a3ec8d1bd274df65d4572969c4a0","tid":249444,"uid":32528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T10:24:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>裂左之後，你要預左唔可以超越以前既狀態，因為會再裂開<br />\n但慢慢一步一步黎 可以回復而家既水平<br />\n無咩風險 可能係做完手術後唔慣之類 <br />\n一兩個月順利行到 半年內做得返運動<br />\n不過我就大約一年先完全正常(強烈都唔會痛)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔可以超越係點解既 再裂係好常見定點<br />\n如果我係比人撞到傷都一樣?"},{"pid":"50eaa0c8873384ce112d31b41eadc121c53b1c90","tid":249444,"uid":32528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T15:03:01.000Z","msg":"仲有側十字partly撕裂"},{"pid":"14d21c76668c03e1be62b871d288f87c7af9c52c","tid":249444,"uid":36906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T15:03:25.000Z","msg":"ibrahim?"},{"pid":"0f28714b127c35d67376b9517e57d68bb4993f13","tid":249444,"uid":81494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T15:10:23.000Z","msg":"如果我做完重建手術半年啦 早排打返波 再整親 骨科醫生話鬆左 咁係咩情況?"},{"pid":"1d29b7c506c4131dad905203a9553962eb3b0da2","tid":249444,"uid":2384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T15:17:50.000Z","msg":"我12月 fully torn 1月頭先做完手術<br />\n對一個做運動既人黎講好似地獄咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf71b187e68fc83738d4918ea5e03bebd57fc694","tid":249444,"uid":32528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T16:06:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我12月 fully torn 1月頭先做完手術<br />\n對一個做運動既人黎講好似地獄咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我就係咁覺得 已經停左個幾月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bdbf974d1f9f1707a016017475c7f911dbfa93d","tid":249444,"uid":27608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T17:14:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>裂左之後，你要預左唔可以超越以前既狀態，因為會再裂開<br />\n但慢慢一步一步黎 可以回復而家既水平<br />\n無咩風險 可能係做完手術後唔慣之類 <br />\n一兩個月順利行到 半年內做得返運動<br />\n不過我就大約一年先完全正常(強烈都唔會痛)</blockquote><br />\n其實超唔超越得返睇你歲數同埋恆心嘅啫<br />\n當然你做返運動嘅時候會有心理陰影令到你唔敢去盡<br />\n睇你敢唔敢去克服"},{"pid":"1a2708903014f2e7d28585bb4642852f171a4c38","tid":249444,"uid":27608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T17:15:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我12月 fully torn 1月頭先做完手術<br />\n對一個做運動既人黎講好似地獄咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我就係咁覺得 已經停左個幾月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去多啲健身室呀<br />\n個人冇咁易肥而且力量都會有進步<br />\n加油啊<br />\n 我上個月斷咗，今個月頭做手術<br />\n依家行路都勉強OK"},{"pid":"153dbbc32076d0806bf333dd47e5b486d0f70850","tid":249444,"uid":50180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T17:24:33.000Z","msg":"數據上黎講大部份人術後6個月會回復返8-9成功能<br />\n<br />\n但前提係要keep住做物理治療同埋睇你手術前有幾fit"},{"pid":"9354283f1a950afd01e974885b7889bed2ee3a28","tid":249444,"uid":15888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T17:31:13.000Z","msg":"最緊要唔好格硬黎, 好返之後D動作都要慢慢試<br />\n衰D講再整到就真係唔洗再打波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:做完年半, 仲未克服到, 唔敢去太盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91676c28b7e354b99f79d1b27ccf24734a6b02e6","tid":249444,"uid":50180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T17:37:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最緊要唔好格硬黎, 好返之後D動作都要慢慢試<br />\n衰D講再整到就真係唔洗再打波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:做完年半, 仲未克服到, 唔敢去太盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打你呢個似係心理影響多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e0435214c91dabac075b681de95461350ed7118","tid":249444,"uid":32528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T17:38:55.000Z","msg":"咁多人都有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問大家住院住左幾耐 同之後幾耐要用supporter行呀?"},{"pid":"bebecdc9a6c98152b43775a4c7fee79fe2dff042","tid":249444,"uid":50180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T17:49:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁多人都有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問大家住院住左幾耐 同之後幾耐要用supporter行呀?</blockquote><br />\nSupporter你係指拐杖？<br />\n大概一至兩個星期"},{"pid":"d0de2e76ba004cd58ebc11e39d4199bf8bc70025","tid":249444,"uid":50180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T17:53:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁多人都有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問大家住院住左幾耐 同之後幾耐要用supporter行呀?</blockquote><br />\nSupporter你係指拐杖？<br />\n大概一至兩個星期</blockquote><br />\n自<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你講knee brace既話 <br />\n要由醫生睇返情況再決定"},{"pid":"aea37b57feabc3ad8dbc47a21e633c297355a8aa","tid":249444,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T17:56:09.000Z","msg":"咁咪兩個月唔返得工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28556068cb3a7daf7e542236eb9e691c16621d14","tid":249444,"uid":34772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T17:57:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁咪兩個月唔返得工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n隻腳唔可以曲同發力姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1245c49243dcf3148ed256499621e526b8f81ef","tid":249444,"uid":2384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T19:11:11.000Z","msg":"我訓左一晚就出院 住院貴 冇保險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個陣好似廢人咁 連上落樓梯都妹下妹下又震晒<br />\n我用左2 3日拐杖就轉用brace 1個月後先叫正常行到<br />\n真係一定一定要做gym  用左4個月先恢復返晒關節幅度 但而家普通射下波上下籃耐左都會痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78cbd7271b5fd31b6ed9bdcaec91399f6d381bbf","tid":249444,"uid":19794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T19:21:06.000Z","msg":"岩岩做完一個月<br />\n公家2月幾3月排<br />\n4月做手術<br />\n依加做完一個月<br />\n有排抖<br />\n其實都無乜特別 又唔會痛<br />\n等八個月後打翻波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5afbff5d766ea87a3a81f8ea2c828a4247d94c8b","tid":249444,"uid":19794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T19:23:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩做完一個月<br />\n公家2月幾3月排<br />\n4月做手術<br />\n依加做完一個月<br />\n有排抖<br />\n其實都無乜特別 又唔會痛<br />\n等八個月後打翻波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我做完手術之後用左叉行路一個禮拜多d<br />\n已經無用 做完手術4個禮拜後先除得個腳托<br />\n因為我mcl都有事 所以要帶4個禮拜<br />\n如果淨係acl 2個星期就除得腳托"},{"pid":"a3e0c85c31f2de9964b517f0a3b644a91b6751f6","tid":249444,"uid":32528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T02:18:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁咪兩個月唔返得工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n隻腳唔可以曲同發力姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/20/101712_4f5922effc401922ee71413d0c1155dc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F20%2F101712_4f5922effc401922ee71413d0c1155dc.jpg&h=e59085b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果咁樣番工 點著suit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  同埋咁應該係術後1至2星期?"},{"pid":"7980f774cb57c43e367d76c016c5e622662eabd7","tid":249444,"uid":43661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T02:31:43.000Z","msg":"06年讀書果陣做過，果陣公立仲係開刀做，兩三個星期後冇用拐杖行，3, 4個月後開始打波，當冇野咁。<br />\n<br />\n之後再斷，一路冇理，早排頂唔順2月係私家做，做完第日出院，而家努力做物理治療同做gym中<br />\n<br />\n而家微創康復好快，普通寫字樓我認1, 2個星期點都返得工，但講真心理點都有影響，好難冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係唯有做物理治療同gym強化肌肉幫下手"}]}